Package: tessera
Title: Accurate Tiling of Spatial Single-Cell Data
Version: 0.1.5
Authors@R: c(
    person("Ilya", "Korsunsky", email = "ilya.korsunsky@gmail.com", 
        role = c("cre", "aut"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-4848-3948")),
    person("Daniel", "Stein", email = "daniel_stein@g.harvard.edu", 
        role = "aut", comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-9442-2604"))
    )
Description: An algorithm for segmenting single-cell resolution
    spatial omics data into small multicellular tiles whose edges track with
    natural tissue boundaries. These tiles can then be used in downstream
    analysis to label and define tissue regions across samples.
URL: https://github.com/korsunskylab/tessera
BugReports: https://github.com/korsunskylab/tessera/issues
License: GPL-3
